description: Experience the epitome of luxury living in this exquisite 2-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence located in the vibrant Seaport District. Boasting a spacious open floor plan, this home features top-of-the-line finishes including 8" wide plank walnut flooring, walnut cabinetry, and a stunning waterfall marble kitchen island. Enjoy breathtaking harbor views from your private balcony and take advantage of first-class amenities such as a fully-equipped gym, golf simulator, 24-hour concierge, doorman, dog spa, resident lounge, fire pit, wet bar, grill, and common terrace. With two garage parking spaces included, convenience is at your fingertips. Located just steps away from Seaport's dining, nightlife, and shopping scene, this residence offers a lifestyle of unparalleled luxury and convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this prestigious property your new home.
